</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[197,1429,1010,1036]" pageId="6" pageNumber="39" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,151,1074]" box="[197,1429,1010,1036]" pageId="6" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,337,1010,1036]" pageId="6" pageNumber="39">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species name is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[858,920,1010,1035]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="39">laxus</emphasis>
(wide) in reference to the wide juxta lobes.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
